  "text": "Because of this background, I once believed that a child’s future depended mainly on intelligence, effort, discipline, and family education.\n\nThrough this program, I have come to understand that development is influenced by many connected factors. Biology, family relationships, culture, school, peers, economic circumstances, and personal experiences all play a part. I now believe that a safe environment and supportive adults can make a meaningful difference by helping a child develop confidence and resilience.",
